48:04.840 --> 48:06.841
(GRUNTING)

48:10.304 --> 48:11.929
(SHRIEKING)

48:12.681 --> 48:14.473
Incoming!

48:14.558 --> 48:15.975
(GRUNTS)

48:23.317 --> 48:26.527
