-(SIRENS WAILING)

48:30.657 --> 48:32.533
ANNOUNCER: Attention,
holiday shoppers!

48:32.618 --> 48:35.119
Don't forget to bring
all your last-minute purchases

48:35.162 --> 48:37.038
to our gift-wrapping department.

48:37.122 --> 48:39.582
Oh, I've never seen it so busy.

48:45.964 --> 48:49.300
Wow, Minnie, who made you
Santa's number-one helper?

48:49.426 --> 48:52.970
Oh, I really want to get Mickey
something special this year.

48:53.430 --> 48:55.598
Without that Christmas bonus,
I'm sunk!

48:55.682 --> 48:56.766
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

48:58.226 --> 49:01.187
Hello? Okey-dokey. Bye.

49:01.480 --> 49:04.649
Mr. Mortimer wants to see you
in his office, right away.

49:05.108 --> 49:07.693
(GASPS) Oh, my Christmas bonus!

49:10.864 --> 49:13.449
-Ginnie!
-Uh, that's Minnie.

49:13.533 --> 49:17.370
Right. I've been making a list
and checking it twice,

49:17.454 --> 49:22.458
and I found that you have been
Santa's best little helper this season!

49:22.751 --> 49:25.836
Your hard work is about to be rewarded.

49:26.129 --> 49:29.507
Close your eyes
and hold out your hands.

49:29.549 --> 49:32.343
Oh, Mr. Mortimer,
I can't thank you enough.

49:32.386 --> 49:35.012
Yes, I know. Now don't interrupt.

49:35.389 --> 49:37.056
-Penny...
-That's Minnie.

49:37.182 --> 49:40.393
Whatever. On behalf of
Mortimer's Department Store,

49:40.477 --> 49:44.271
it gives me great pleasure
to present you with your

49:44.356 --> 49:46.148
Christmas bonus!

49:46.233 --> 49:47.483
-(MINNIE GRUNTS)
-(THUDS)

49:48.402 --> 49:50.361
A fruitcake?

49:50.404 --> 49:51.737
No need to thank me.

49:51.822 --> 49:55.574
The expression on your face
is thanks enough. (CHUCKLES)

49:55.742 --> 49:57.201
And now, scoot along.

49:57.244 --> 50:00.121
Back to the gift-wrapping department,
where you belong.

50:00.455 --> 50:04.000
Oh, and, Winnie. Merry Christmas!

50:08.505 --> 50:09.714
Oh, Mickey.

50:10.298 --> 50:13.509
How am I ever going to get
your present now?

50:14.678 --> 50:18.139
There's just gotta be a way
to get Minnie's present by 5:00.

50:18.557 --> 50:19.557
(PLAYING)

50:23.520 --> 50:24.854
You got any ideas, fella?

50:27.774 --> 50:28.816
(WHIMPERING)

50:28.900 --> 50:31.193
Don't worry, boy.
We'll come up with something.

50:31.778 --> 50:32.945
We just gotta.

50:33.030 --> 50:34.905
(PLAYING)

50:49.129 --> 50:51.797
Do you think the band
will ever show up?

50:51.840 --> 50:52.923
I don't know.

50:52.966 --> 50:55.801
They're putting out a fire
at the Crazy Pete Tree Lot.

50:55.886 --> 50:58.137
Just went up like a Roman candle.

51:00.015 --> 51:01.515
FIREFIGHTER: Uh, Chief?

51:01.600 --> 51:04.518
Looks like the toy drive's a big fat bust.

51:06.188 --> 51:07.813
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

51:07.856 --> 51:09.273
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

51:09.316 --> 51:11.776
Listen! That music!

51:12.152 --> 51:14.153
(GASPS) Come on!

51:18.658 --> 51:19.992
(GRUNTS)

51:21.203 --> 51:22.495
Hmm?

51:22.704 --> 51:26.457
MICKEY: Where we going, fellas?
FIRE CHIEF: A concert in the park.

51:27.250 --> 51:29.043
Oh, look, bub. We're desperate.

51:29.127 --> 51:32.588
We need music for the toy drive,
and you're our only hope!

51:32.672 --> 51:35.633
I don't have time, Chief.
I gotta get a gift for my girl.

51:35.675 --> 51:38.177
Look, pally, don't do it for us.

51:38.220 --> 51:40.137
-Do it for the kids.
-But I...

51:40.180 --> 51:42.306
Look, son. To these kids,

51:42.349 --> 51:46.560
the only difference between
a broken heart and a smile is you!

51:47.354 --> 51:49.396
You're on! Break a leg, pal.

51:54.402 --> 51:56.237
(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)

52:03.703 --> 52:06.705
Look, I'm really sorry, but I can't stay.

52:06.790 --> 52:09.667
I got some Christmas shopping
to do, you know, and...

52:15.924 --> 52:17.049
Gosh.

52:21.221 --> 52:22.972
(PLAYING)

52:57.507 --> 52:58.966
(TROMBONE PLAYING)

53:05.765 --> 53:06.974
The band is back!

53:07.058 --> 53:09.435
FIREFIGHTER: Must have been
a hot one at Crazy Pete's.

53:44.804 --> 53:45.846
(ALL CHEERING)

53:50.101 --> 53:52.311
Well, guess I'll be
showing up at Minnie's empty-handed.

53:52.395 --> 53:54.396
That was terrific!

53:54.522 --> 53:57.983
(CHUCKLES) Thanks to you,
this was our best toy drive ever!

53:58.026 --> 54:00.986
You and that harmonica
sure make a great team.

54:01.321 --> 54:04.365
Yup. She's worth her weight
in gold, all right! (CHUCKLES)

54:06.368 --> 54:08.202
Holy cow! That's it!

54:08.662 --> 54:11.497
We've still got two minutes
to get to the shop!

54:11.539 --> 54:13.082
-Come on, Pluto!
-(BARKING)

54:13.166 --> 54:15.376
-Thanks, fellas!
-Goodbye!

54:15.460 --> 54:17.461
-FIREFIGHTER: Thanks again!
-WOMAN: Merry Christmas!

54:36.856 --> 54:37.856
(HORN HONKING)

54:42.404 --> 54:43.946
(YAWNING)

54:44.030 --> 54:45.197
Sorry!

54:50.161 --> 54:51.829
MICKEY: Hey! What's going on?

54:53.164 --> 54:54.415
(HORN HONKING)

54:55.083 --> 54:56.083
Whoa!

54:59.379 --> 55:00.379
(WHIMPERS)

55:05.385 --> 55:06.719
This is our stop!

55:08.054 --> 55:09.054
(BOTH GRUNT)

55:09.306 --> 55:11.098
Oh, look! There's the shop.

55:25.780 --> 55:27.990
(BELL TINKLING)

55:28.533 --> 55:30.284
Oh, excuse me, sir.

55:30.368 --> 55:34.330
I was just hoping to trade this
for a gift for my girl.

55:38.793 --> 55:41.837
Well, sorry, son.
That harmonica isn't worth much.

55:43.840 --> 55:45.215
Well, merry Christmas.

55:47.469 --> 55:50.095
You're worth a lot to me, old friend.

55:54.976 --> 55:57.102
(PLAYING)

55:58.063 --> 55:59.521
(HOWLING)

56:11.785 --> 56:13.285
(GROANS)

56:16.081 --> 56:20.709
Say, maybe that harmonica
is worth something after all.

56:21.628 --> 56:23.545
Come on in. Come on in.

56:34.516 --> 56:35.891
(PLUTO BARKING)

56:36.476 --> 56:37.935
-(PANTING)
-(MEOWS)

56:38.228 --> 56:40.145
MICKEY: Can't wait
to open your present, can you, boy?

56:40.647 --> 56:42.064
(CHUCKLES) I know just how you feel.

56:42.148 --> 56:43.649
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah!

56:45.318 --> 56:47.986
Oh! I love Christmas so much!

56:48.655 --> 56:52.157
Say, Mickey,
why don't you play some music?

56:52.659 --> 56:53.659
(LAUGHS)

56:53.743 --> 56:56.120
Isn't it time we were
opening our presents?

56:56.162 --> 56:59.832
And, speaking of time, what time is it?

57:00.792 --> 57:04.336
Well, I think it's time
for you to open your gift.

57:13.221 --> 57:17.182
Oh! A case for my harmonica.

57:17.725 --> 57:21.520
Oh, my! A chain for my watch.

57:21.563 --> 57:23.647
Oh, Mickey, it's beautiful.

57:24.649 --> 57:27.651
